NG0045:437: byar med rtsol bral ngas bstan gyis //
NG0045:438: rdo rje sems dpas yid la zung *//
NG0045:439: bsgrub med rtsol bsgrub smon pa med pa yi //

NG0045:441: bya bral nam mkha' ji bzhin te //
NG0045:442: rtsol bsgrub bya btsal ga la yod //
NG0045:443: gsal dag ye shes dgongs pa 'di //
NG0045:444: rang byung ngang dngas 'od gsal yin //
NG0045:445: btang ngo bzhag go rang bzhin de //
NG0045:446: blang dor brod pa bskyed mi bya //
NG0045:447: mngon sum mi snang rgyab nas 'byung *//
NG0045:448: phra zhing shes dka'i chos 'di ni //
NG0045:449: rnam par mi rtog rtog las 'das //
NG0045:450: sku gcig kun tu khyab pas bsnan pa'i chos med de //
NG0045:451: sems dang chos ni ci yang ma yin pas //

NG0045:453: kun gzhi klong yangs chos dbyings nas //
NG0045:454: rig yid sems blo ci byung yang *//
NG0045:455: thol byung ngang dngas byung sar thim //

NG0045:458: 'gyur ba med pa'i rgya yis thob //
NG0045:459: sems kyi rang bzhin ci yang ma yin pas //

NG0045:482: a ka da t-i sa tis hri ti b+ho ya hri ta /
NG0045:484: gsang sngags ngo bo brda' yis @#//
NG0045:486: sngon thog skye med gtan gzhi'i gnas //
NG0045:487: rgyal yul chos nyid yangs pa na //
NG0045:488: khri rje yang gsal spyi phud bzhugs //

NG0045:493: rang byung ngang dngas ye gsal bzhugs //
NG0045:494: gsal dag spros gcod 'khor gyis bskor //
NG0045:495: zhing khams yongs la mnga' yang mdzad //

NG0045:502: brgyad khri bzhi stong 'khor longs spyod //
NG0045:503: kun 'byung spyi sa'i ldum ra na //
NG0045:504: bsam 'phel nor bu rin chen yod //

NG0045:512: mi yi nor bu rin chen la //
NG0045:513: rang byung rig yid dran sems blo //
NG0045:514: thol byung ngang dngas rin du bcol //
NG0045:515: bsam 'phel nor bu thob par gyis //
NG0045:516: spros gcod rang grol rgya yis thob //
NG0045:517: yang snying bdud rtsi'i bcud cig 'thung *//
NG0045:518: bcud 'thung yang snying thugs la chongs //
NG0045:520: byar med bde chen dbyings su nyol //
NG0045:524: gsang sngags brda'i le'u ste bcu pa'o ///
NG0045:525: / de nas rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NG0045:526: kun bzang nyid la 'di skad zhus //
NG0045:527: theg pa'i spyi phud spyi ti ru //

NG0045:530: ston pas 'khor la bka' stsal pa //
NG0045:531: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NG0045:532: kun bzang yangs pa rnam dag snying po'i klong *//
NG0045:533: mi skye mi 'gag snying po rang sar grol //
NG0045:534: rdzogs dang ma rdzogs gzhi la gnyis med kyang *//
NG0045:535: rtsal zer yan lag chos rnams rdzogs lugs ni //
NG0045:537: 'jig rten sa la gnyis te skye bo dang *//
NG0045:538: grub mtha' log pa'i phyi rol mu stegs pa'o //

NG0045:540: mkha' klong rnam dag snying po bcud spungs su //
NG0045:541: rtsal zer 'gag med chos rnams yongs rdzogs te //
NG0045:542: gzhi gnas rang dngas rang sangs so //
NG0045:543: bde chen mi rtog rang sangs pas //
NG0045:544: gzung 'dzin dri med dgag bsgrub med //

NG0045:546: snang ba chen po gsal ba yin //

NG0045:549: rtag pa'i lta ba ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:550: 'das pa'i theg pa dgu yi rdzogs lugs ni //
NG0045:552: sems gnyis su ma grub pas //
NG0045:553: nyan thos lta ba ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:554: rten 'brel rnam par rig byed med //
NG0045:555: rang rgyal lta ba ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:556: phyi nang gzung 'dzin gnyis med pas //
NG0045:557: sems tsam lta ba ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:558: bden gnyis kha tshon bcad du med //
NG0045:559: dbu ma'i lta ba ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:560: phyi rgyud sde gsum rdzogs lugs ni //
NG0045:561: phyi ltar snang ba'i rnam pa la //
NG0045:562: phyi dag nang dag rdzas dag las //
NG0045:563: kri ya'i lta ba ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:564: mar spyod yar blta'i rtsis gdab med //
NG0045:565: u pa ya yi lta ba rdzogs //
NG0045:566: 'di ltar snang ba'i yul rnams la //
NG0045:567: chos 'phrul lnga dang rigs gsum mgon //
NG0045:568: cho 'phrul rtsis gdab bya rtsol med //
NG0045:569: yo ga'i lta ba ma lus rdzogasas //
NG0045:570: 'di ltar phyi nang snod bcud kyang *//
NG0045:571: ting 'dzin rnam gsum sgor zhugs nas //
NG0045:572: yo byad lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi //
NG0045:573: yongs su brtags nas lha ru bsgom //
NG0045:574: snod kyi 'jig rten snang ba la //
NG0045:575: phung po rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sku //
NG0045:576: 'byung ba lnga ni rigs yum lnga //
NG0045:577: tshogs brgyad sems dpa' sems mar snang *//
NG0045:578: khams dang skye mched lha lha mo //
NG0045:579: skye mched mu bzhi sgo ba sgo ma bzhi //
NG0045:580: snang la mi 'gog thabs yin te //
NG0045:581: rang bzhin med pa shes rab yin //
NG0045:582: gnyis med thad du 'brel pas na //
NG0045:583: ma ha'i lta ba yongs su rdzogs //
NG0045:584: rgyu ni dag pa'i dbyings su blta //
NG0045:586: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med pas //
NG0045:587: a nu'i lta ba yongs su rdzogs //
NG0045:588: snang ba sku yi dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NG0045:589: grag pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NG0045:590: dran rtog thugs kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NG0045:592: thams cad yongs rdzogs rdzogs pa che //
NG0045:593: 'jug sgo phrin las dkyil 'khor dbang dam rdzogs //
NG0045:594: lha bskyed spyan 'dren 'dzab dang gtor ma rdzogs //
NG0045:595: gshegs gsol smon lam rgyas 'debs thams cad rdzogs //
NG0045:596: lta sgom spyod 'bras sku dang ye shes rdzogs //
NG0045:597: sa lam ye shes phra rags man ngag rdzogs //
NG0045:598: rgyud lung man ngag dam tshig sdom pa rdzogs //
NG0045:599: lam lnga sa bcu pha rol phyin bcu rdzogs //
NG0045:600: thams cad rdzogs pa'i spyi ti yo ga yin //
NG0045:601: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NG0045:602: 'gyu ba ma yin drang por rdzogs //
NG0045:605: rdzogs lugs bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ///
NG0045:606: / swa ti a ti sarba ra tsa hri ti b+ho ya /
NG0045:607: de nas rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NG0045:608: dgu rtse spyi rgyal spy-i ti ru //
NG0045:609: thams cad yongs rdzogs ji ltar lags //
NG0045:611: ston pas 'khor la bka' stsal pa //
NG0045:615: mkha' dbyings rnam dag kun 'byung klong yangs nas //
NG0045:616: dgag bsgrub gnyis med rang grol zang thal bas //
NG0045:617: snang srid 'khor 'das btags chags chos rnams rdzogs //
NG0045:620: tha snyad brgyad khri bzhi stong ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:621: spang len chags sdang dbye bsal gnyis med pas //
NG0045:622: yod med rtag chad 'gro ba rigs drug rdzogs //
NG0045:623: lta ba tshig bral phyogs ris med //
NG0045:624: blos btags lta ba ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:625: ye dag ma bcos ngang dag pas //
NG0045:626: tha mal dran bsam 'gyu ba bral //
NG0045:627: yid bzung sgom pa ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:628: rang byung rnam dag ma bcos par //
NG0045:629: lus ngag yid gsum rtsol med de //
NG0045:630: ma chags ma btsal klong yangs su //
NG0045:631: ched byas spyod pa ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:632: ye sangs snying po'i bcud 'dus pas //
NG0045:633: spang thob med pa'i thig le ru //
NG0045:634: yid smon 'bras bu ma lus rdzogs //
NG0045:635: lta ba stong gsal 'gyur ba med //
NG0045:636: sgom pa 'od gsal dmigs pa med //
NG0045:637: spyod pa byar med chags sdang med //
NG0045:638: 'bras bu ka dag yid smon med //
NG0045:639: gnad gcig gis ni gnad rnams thams cad grol //
NG0045:640: don gcig gis ni don rnams thams cad gtan la 'bebs //
NG0045:641: brda' gcig gis ni brda' rnams thams cad grol //
NG0045:642: tshig gcig shes pas tha snyad ma lus shes //
NG0045:643: theg pa gcig gi sgor zhugs rtogs pa yis //
NG0045:644: brgyad khri bzhi stong rtogs pa'i man ngag yin //
NG0045:645: e ma'o sangs rgyas spyod yul 'di //
NG0045:646: btsal bas rnyed pa'i gnas med do //
NG0045:647: rtog med mnyam nyid chos ky-i+i sku //
NG0045:648: bzung bas mi zin chu zla 'dra //
NG0045:649: bya bral nam mkha' ji bzhin te //
NG0045:650: gcig gi rnam pa yongs kyi med //
NG0045:651: rnal 'byor bya bral nam mkhar gnas //
NG0045:652: ma byung ma skyes snying po la //
NG0045:653: sgro btags chos kun ga la yod //
NG0045:654: ci ste lam la bgrod gyur na //
NG0045:655: nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin thug pa med //
NG0045:658: spyi ti yo ga bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ///
NG0045:659: / de nas rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NG0045:660: kun bzang nyid la 'di skad zhus //
NG0045:661: mtshan dang gtad rgya ji ltar lags //
NG0045:663: ston pas 'khor la bka' stsal pa //
NG0045:664: snying po ming med ming dang bral //

NG0045:666: dus gsum sangs rgyas gsang ba'i bcud phyung bas //
NG0045:667: snying po bcud spungs thig le 'dus pa'i rgyud //

NG0045:669: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i rgyud //

NG0045:672: bskal pa stong du bsags pa'i mun pa rnams //
NG0045:673: rin chen nyi zlas sel bas nyi zla 'bar //
NG0045:674: theg pa spyi 'grel spyi ti yo ga'i rgyud //
NG0045:675: chos sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong gnya' gcog pas //
NG0045:676: rdzogs chen rgyal po spyi ti yo gar zung *//
NG0045:677: theg pa rnams kyi dgu rtse spyi rgyal 'di //

NG0045:679: dad mos brtson ldan ma chags ser sna med //
NG0045:680: nyon mongs chung zhing byang chub sgrub la @#//
NG0045:682: dregs shing mkhas 'dod mu cor smra ba dang *//
NG0045:683: don la mi bsgom tshig zol zong du 'tshong *//
NG0045:684: de la bstan na gnyis ka dmyal bar ltung *//
NG0045:685: de bas man ngag shin tu gsang ba gces //
NG0045:688: dus dang mtshan dang gtad rgya bstan pa'i le'u ste
NG0045:689: bcu gsum pa'o // // dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NG0045:690: thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pa /
